## 📌 6. DB 스키마 요약

### Users
`{ _id, email, googleId, displayName, profileImage, passwordHash(nullable), createdAt, updatedAt }`

### Cats
`{ _id, userId(→User), name, birthDate, weight, preExistingConditions:[] }`

### ScanLogs (타임라인 핵심)
`{ _id, userId, catId, type(PLANT|INGREDIENT|CHAT|SYMPTOM|HOSPITAL), content, riskLevel(SAFE|WARNING|TOXIC|NONE), scanData(Mixed/JSON, 스캔 결과 전체), memo(String), imageUrl, palatabilityRating(1~5), timestamp }`

### ToxicityDB (독성 사전)
`{ itemName, itemNameKo, aliases:[], category(PLANT|FOOD|CHEMICAL), toxicityLevel(HIGH|MEDIUM|LOW), symptoms:[], description }`

